兩次就無</blockquote><br />\n外國睇幾錢?<br />\n之前黎香港太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有嚟過香港咩？60年代同beatles個陣？<br />\n佢嚟亞洲開live應該就淨係去日本？"},{"pid":"8143dc68aa0b7f75bcdfd51f131a113c5e1f0ad8","tid":412592,"uid":13821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想去佢 live ，有冇介紹 ，真心，去佢live 係我嘅願望</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇就應該係隔年嚟日本，13, 15, 17 可能19再嚟掛<br />\n如果去聽記得一定要去幾日<br />\nband on the run, hey jude嗰啲每日必唱<br />\nday tripper, get back個啲唔係成日有"},{"pid":"55eef9e7464cf75b5f262cfacef19917a41e4392","tid":412592,"uid":13821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好想去佢 live ，有冇介紹 ，真心，去佢live 係我嘅願望</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇就應該係隔年嚟日本，13, 15, 17 可能19再嚟掛<br />\n如果去聽記得一定要去幾日<br />\nband on the run, hey jude嗰啲每日必唱<br />\nday tripper, get back個啲唔係成日有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十二月會去Australia live，唔知網上幾時開始開賣<br />\n我個陣就早兩個月網上開賣第一日夜晚六七點買嘅，買個陣都無乜靚位，屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得記得一開賣即刻第一時間上網買如果唔係就好似我咁坐山頂位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/020855_90073a045283463a56c8080765e74a03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F020855_90073a045283463a56c8080765e74a03.png&h=8da3d060&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19e8c696ea40153b46f76e2a02da593b767c2fcb","tid":412592,"uid":59312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成70幾歳人重唱咁高音<br />\n係咪癡撚線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好想睇，驚佢老人家佢年紀大</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n係就快啦，12月好似去澳洲<br />\n佢都75，可能搞多一兩次就無</blockquote><br />\n外國睇幾錢?<br />\n之前黎香港太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有嚟過香港咩？60年代同beatles個陣？<br />\n佢嚟亞洲開live應該就淨係去日本？</blockquote><br />\n冇黎過㗎? 我唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我有印象賣二三千蚊一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}